The Table Mountain Aerial Cableway is proud to announce the launch of its private cable car service to make your next visit extra special. This new offering is ideal for those wishing to have an extra level of social distancing and privacy when hosting their event, special occasion or private group on top of Africa’s leading tourist attraction Table Mountain is one of the world’s iconic natural wonders, drawing millions of visitors to its slopes every year. The Table Mountain Aerial Cableway is proud to announce the launch of its private cable car service to make your next visit extra special. This new offering is ideal for those wishing to have an extra level of social distancing and privacy when hosting their event, special occasion or private group on top of Africa’s leading tourist attraction. “Our commitment has and will always be to ensure memorable moments at the Cableway, which is why we’re proud to include this as part of our offering,” says Giselle Esau, Cableway executive manager of brand and marketing. Your experience starts the moment you arrive at Africa’s very own New7Wonder of Nature. Skipping the queues, you will be escorted to the private cable car you will be using exclusively for your return trip. Once inside, you will get to enjoy a breathtaking ride up the mountain and amazing 360-degree views from the top. The private-car experience can be booked online via Webtickets. Tickets can only be redeemed from Monday to Friday during the Cableway’s regular operating hours.